"{\"uid\": \"examiner.com.au-story-8730867-tasmanian-hero-ariarne-titmus-shines-at-paris-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"It's fair to say Ariarne Titmus has made Australia proud, but she's made Tasmanian even prouder.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 96, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 41, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.999999873188707, \"rank\": 9.37630893694576e-08, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  The Launceston-born swimmer returned from the 2024 Paris Olympics Games with two gold medals and two silver.\", \"from\": 98, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When Titmus won gold in the 2021 Tokyo Olympic Games, the whole of Sacred Heart Primary school watched her compete, and for good reason - because the Olympic champion was one of their own.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus attended the school from kindergarten to grade six, and current principal Brent Wilson said she returned to her old stomping grounds shortly after the 2021 Olympics.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Brent\", \"score\": 0.9992357303526911, \"rank\": 0.000699953725734813, \"text\": \"Brent\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Brent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Borough_of_Brent\"}, {\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9910798976450116, \"rank\": 0.009000040527931621, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ariarne visited the school, and we interviewed her.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She gave up quite a bit of her time,\\\" Mr Wilson said.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9910798976450116, \"rank\": 0.009000040527931621, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She spent two or three hours signing autographs with the kids and doing all those good things.\\\"\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Wilson said Titmus had an \\\"absolutely sensational personality\\\", and she inspired the students.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9910798976450116, \"rank\": 0.009000040527931621, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was really welcoming.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She gave everybody the time they sought from her,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a champions wall, and she signed that - the kids walked away knowing she's one of our girls.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We proudly put that on Facebook after she won her first gold in the Paris Olympics - her mum actually liked it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Wilson said Titmus was still the humble and friendly person she was as a student.\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9910798976450116, \"rank\": 0.009000040527931621, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People tell me her personality has not changed; she was always friendly and well-liked by everyone,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Growing up, Titmus swam with Riverside Swim Club and frequently attended the Launceston Aquatic Centre, where a pool was named after her.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Aquatic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Launceston Aquatic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Aquatic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Aquatic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Wilson said Titmus was a shining example of believing in what you do and aiming for the stars.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"score\": 0.9910798976450116, \"rank\": 0.009000040527931621, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Woodrow_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The kids see her as one of us,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If a student from Sacred Heart can achieve that, that's what they aspire to.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sacred_Heart\", \"score\": 0.9999713479999842, \"rank\": 2.8634278565174197e-05, \"text\": \"Sacred Heart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sacred_Heart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sacred_Heart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether that's in swimming or something else.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Titmus is equal third in Australia's all-time medal tally.\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Titmus\"}, {\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.999999873188707, \"rank\": 9.37630893694576e-08, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Northern Tasmania born and bred.\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"School reporter, interested also in the Launceston music scene.\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1957, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Football_Club\", \"score\": 0.9999999949432095, \"rank\": 4.8834961228526296e-09, \"text\": \"Launceston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Football_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Launceston_Football_Club\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"E